Executive Summary


Troubles that occurred during the project:
1: We had a lot of duplicates on the staging table and I had to use the Row Number to eliminate the duplicates and take only the latest record into our ODS and further to the DW.
2: While working on the DimProper Manager data we realized that we had a lot of empty spaces coming from the source. The data percentage was huge, so instead of eliminating all those records, we chose to use ‘Not Listed’ instead of leaving those empty.
3: While loading the JSON file, we noticed that a few bit columns in the source had empty spaces instead of a flag value. We replaced the missing values with 0.
